data.description:
Positioned just a stone's throw away from the hubbub of metropolitan excitement, this charming home stands as an oasis of peaceful retreat, conveniently proximate to all essential amenities and recreational opportunities you could wish for. 

A variety of trees and landscaping frame the front porch for pleasing appeal that sets the tone for this home. The versatile floor layout caters to all lifestyle requisites, offering a multifunctional room ideally suited to functioning as either an efficient home workspace or a dining room. 

Commanding the central space of the house is the sizeable family room - a nucleus of togetherness that radiates an atmosphere of comfort, underscored by the soft, natural light permeating the entire space. This room provides the perfect backdrop for unhurried moments of relaxation, as well as sparkly social engagements characterized by animated conversations.

Adjacent to this lies the kitchen that showcases an effortless layout which eases meal preparation, turning the often mundane chore into a delightful experience. 

The staircase leads to a roomy loft, a versatile space brimming with opportunities for recreation or simply carving out a quaint, personal retreat. This added living quarter, waiting for your creative touch, guarantees every family member their own unique sanctuary 

A distinct hallmark of this property is its generous backyard - an escape from the routine hustle and bustle of everyday life. Here there is a covered patio in addition to an open wood deck. It offers limitless possibilities: perhaps a lush, colorful garden, a secure children's play area, or even the addition of your very own private pool.
